{"tid":987693,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術］信用卡 點解要夠指定金額先可以用？","createTime":"2019-01-19T13:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T13:30:24.000Z","uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"836a3972ba0db2b74b7305102024e365958dafe3","tid":987693,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的今晚同男友食飯賣單時 <br />\n餐廳話要滿300$ 先可以用信用卡 <br />\n<br />\n咁就引申左我同佢討論依個問題<br />\n<br />\n信用卡一般會收鋪頭單一交易既 3%固定手續費<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得係 <br />\n因為 鋪頭 做一單$100既生意既利潤率，<br />\n係會少於一單$300既利潤率。<br />\n<br />\n而我男友 就覺得我咁諗係唔岩<br />\n佢話 手續費係固定% 點解一定滿指定金額先可以用<br />\n<br />\n請教各巴絲解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fd0771c7d8f08d8bcf36ee36a4ecb4eaa8b256","tid":987693,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb2549cf301960ab4501e4779995d938351e66c","tid":987693,"uid":127929,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"你條仔冇撚用架!揾過第二個啦!"},{"pid":"670562577cae9c5ff0849011d50c3caeee3caa3c","tid":987693,"uid":205105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cb2549cf301960ab4501e4779995d938351e66c","tid":987693,"uid":127929,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"你條仔冇撚用架!揾過第二個啦!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27e4aaa1bb158e487bc426e8651a62af7564f22","tid":987693,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"認真討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f19aad7b59a95b8a215695c9bcd57bbd8ebef74","tid":987693,"uid":87820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"你岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmo